---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro'
---

<Layout title="About George-AI" description="Learn about George-AI and our mission">
  <h1 class="text-4xl font-bold mb-8">About George-AI</h1>

  <article class="max-w-3xl prose prose-lg">
    <h2 class="text-3xl font-semibold mt-8 mb-4">What is George-AI?</h2>
    <p class="text-gray-700 leading-relaxed">
      George-AI is a self-hosted RAG (Retrieval-Augmented Generation) platform
      that helps organizations leverage AI with their own data while maintaining
      full control and data sovereignty.
    </p>

    <h2 class="text-3xl font-semibold mt-8 mb-4">Key Features</h2>
    <ul class="space-y-2 text-gray-700 leading-relaxed">
      <li>Multi-source data ingestion (email, web, files, SharePoint, SMB)</li>
      <li>AI-powered processing with embeddings and vector search</li>
      <li>Enterprise integration with n8n workflows</li>
      <li>Self-hosted deployment with multi-tenant support</li>
      <li>EU AI Act compliance features</li>
    </ul>
  </article>
</Layout>
